---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    fontSize: 18px
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Aluno
    participant Browser as Frontend<br/>(ChatDiary)
    participant Backend as Backend Laravel<br/>(ChatTurnProcessor)
    participant Classifier as BranchClassifier
    participant LLM as Provedor LLM<br/>(OpenAi / Gemini / Ollama)
    participant Queue as Fila Laravel
    participant Job as Job<br/>AnalyzeDiaryResponse
    actor Professor

    Aluno->>Browser: Inicia diário da aula
    Browser->>Backend: GET /lessons/{id}
    Backend->>Backend: Cria LessonResponse<br/>(status: em andamento)
    Backend-->>Browser: Mensagem inicial do bot

    loop A cada turno do aluno
        Aluno->>Browser: Envia resposta
        Browser->>Backend: POST mensagem
        Backend->>Backend: Persiste ChatMessage (role=student)

        alt Nó com múltiplas arestas (free_text)
            Backend->>Classifier: classifyBranch(question, answer, edges)
            Classifier->>LLM: payload JSON + prompt v3
            LLM-->>Classifier: { edge_id }
            Classifier-->>Backend: BranchDecision + prompt_version_id
        else free_talk
            Backend->>Classifier: classifyEngagement(answer, recent_turns)
            Classifier->>LLM: payload JSON
            LLM-->>Classifier: { engagement_level, decision, rationale }
            Classifier-->>Backend: EngagementDecision
        end

        Backend->>Backend: Resolve próximo nó<br/>e persiste ChatMessage (role=bot)
        Backend-->>Browser: Próxima fala do bot
    end

    Note over Backend: Aluno atinge nó end<br/>ou cap de mensagens
    Backend->>Backend: Verificação final<br/>(há algo mais a compartilhar?)
    Backend->>Backend: Consolida LessonResponse.content<br/>e marca submitted_at
    Backend->>Queue: dispatch(AnalyzeDiaryResponse)
    Backend-->>Browser: Encerra sessão

    Queue->>Job: handle()
    Job->>LLM: prompt diary-analysis +<br/>conteúdo consolidado
    LLM-->>Job: JSON estruturado<br/>(resumo, indicadores, listas)
    Job->>Job: Atualiza DiaryAnalysis<br/>(status: completed)
    Job->>Job: dispatch DiaryAnalysisUpdated

    Professor->>Backend: GET /diaries/{response}
    Backend-->>Professor: Análise + LessonResponse

    alt Aprovar
        Professor->>Backend: approveAnalysis(notes)
        Backend->>Backend: status = approved
    else Rejeitar
        Professor->>Backend: rejectAnalysis(notes)
        Backend->>Backend: status = rejected
    end
